<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ar" dir="rtl" id="htmlTag">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
<title>محوّل الرحلات v2.6 — Al-Mosafer</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=IBM+Plex+Sans+Arabic:wght@300;400;500;600&family=IBM+Plex+Mono:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
*,*::before,*::after{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0;}
:root{
  --slate:#0f172a;--slate-mid:#1e293b;
  --emerald:#10b981;--emerald-d:#059669;
  --emerald-x:rgba(16,185,129,0.12);--emerald-b:rgba(16,185,129,0.28);
  --sky:#38bdf8;--amber:#f59e0b;
  --bg:#f0f4f8;--white:#ffffff;
  --border:rgba(0,0,0,0.07);--border-s:rgba(0,0,0,0.12);
  --text:#0f172a;--muted:#64748b;--faint:#94a3b8;
  --radius:12px;--radius-sm:8px;
  --shadow:0 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,0.06),0 1px 2px rgba(0,0,0,0.04);
}
body{font-family:'IBM Plex Sans Arabic','Segoe UI',Tahoma,sans-serif;background:var(--bg);color:var(--text);min-height:100vh;}
.app-shell{display:grid;grid-template-columns:60px 1fr;min-height:100vh;}
@media(max-width:768px){.app-shell{grid-template-columns:1fr;}.icon-sidebar{display:none;}}
.icon-sidebar{background:var(--slate);display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;padding:14px 0;gap:4px;position:sticky;top:0;height:100vh;z-index:20;}
.sb-logo{width:36px;height:36px;background:var(--emerald);border-radius:10px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;margin-bottom:14px;flex-shrink:0;font-size:1.2rem;}
.sb-spacer{flex:1;}
.sb-version{font-size:9px;color:#334155;writing-mode:vertical-rl;letter-spacing:0.05em;margin-bottom:8px;}
.sb-icon{width:40px;height:40px;border-radius:10px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;color:#475569;font-size:18px;cursor:pointer;transition:.18s;position:relative;}
.sb-icon:hover{background:rgba(255,255,255,0.07);color:#94a3b8;}
.sb-icon.active{background:rgba(16,185,129,0.15);color:var(--emerald);}
.sb-icon[data-tip]:hover::after{content:attr(data-tip);position:absolute;right:calc(100% + 10px);top:50%;transform:translateY(-50%);background:var(--slate-mid);color:#e2e8f0;font-size:11px;padding:4px 8px;border-radius:6px;white-space:nowrap;pointer-events:none;z-index:99;font-family:'IBM Plex Sans Arabic',sans-serif;}
.main-panel{display:flex;flex-direction:column;min-height:100vh;overflow:hidden;}
.topbar{background:var(--white);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);padding:0 20px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;min-height:54px;position:sticky;top:0;z-index:10;box-shadow:var(--shadow);}
.topbar-title{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;}
.topbar-badge{background:var(--slate);color:var(--emerald);font-size:11px;font-weight:700;padding:3px 10px;border-radius:20px;font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace;}
.topbar-h{font-size:15px;font-weight:600;color:var(--text);}
.topbar-h span{color:var(--emerald);}
.pb-right{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;}
.lang-toggle{display:flex;background:var(--bg);border-radius:8px;padding:3px;gap:2px;}
.lang-btn{padding:4px 12px;border-radius:6px;border:none;font-family:inherit;font-size:12px;cursor:pointer;background:transparent;color:var(--muted);font-weight:500;transition:.15s;}
.lang-btn.active{background:var(--white);color:var(--text);box-shadow:var(--shadow);}
.body-layout{display:grid;grid-template-columns:320px 1fr;gap:0;flex:1;min-height:0;}
@media(max-width:900px){.body-layout{grid-template-columns:1fr;}.input-panel{max-height:none;}}
.input-panel{background:var(--white);border-left:1px solid var(--border);display:flex;flex-direction:column;overflow-y:auto;max-height:calc(100vh - 54px);position:sticky;top:54px;}
.ip-section{border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);padding:16px;}
.ip-section:last-child{border-bottom:none;flex:1;}
.ip-title{font-size:11px;font-weight:600;color:var(--muted);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.06em;margin-bottom:10px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;}
.ip-title-dot{width:6px;height:6px;border-radius:50%;flex-shrink:0;}
.ip-textarea{width:100%;background:#f8fafc;border:1px solid var(--border-s);border-radius:var(--radius-sm);color:var(--text);font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace;font-size:11px;line-height:1.6;padding:8px 10px;resize:vertical;transition:.15s;min-height:110px;outline:none;}
.ip-textarea:focus{border-color:var(--emerald);background:#fff;box-shadow:0 0 0 3px var(--emerald-x);}
.ip-textarea::placeholder{color:var(--faint);}
.fmt-helper{background:#eff6ff;border:1px solid #bfdbfe;border-radius:8px;padding:9px 11px;margin-bottom:10px;}
.fmt-helper summary{cursor:pointer;font-size:11px;font-weight:600;color:#1d4ed8;list-style:none;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:5px;}
.fmt-tabs{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:4px;margin:7px 0 5px;}
.fmt-tab{padding:3px 9px;border-radius:4px;border:1px solid #bfdbfe;background:#fff;cursor:pointer;font-size:10px;font-weight:700;color:#1d4ed8;transition:.12s;}
.fmt-tab.active,.fmt-tab:hover{background:#1d4ed8;color:#fff;border-color:#1d4ed8;}
.fmt-example{background:#fff;border:1px dashed #bfdbfe;border-radius:5px;padding:7px 9px;font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace;font-size:10px;line-height:1.65;white-space:pre-wrap;display:none;color:#334155;}
.fmt-example.active{display:block;}
.use-example-btn{background:#1d4ed8;color:#fff;border:none;border-radius:4px;padding:3px 10px;cursor:pointer;font-size:10px;font-family:inherit;font-weight:700;margin-top:5px;transition:.12s;}
.use-example-btn:hover{background:#1e40af;}
.parse-status{padding:7px 10px;border-radius:7px;font-size:11px;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:8px;}
.parse-ok{background:#f0fdf4;color:#15803d;border:1px solid #bbf7d0;}
.parse-warn{background:#fffbeb;color:#92400e;border:1px solid #fde68a;}
.parse-err{background:#fff1f2;color:#9f1239;border:1px solid #fecdd3;}
.btn-extract{width:100%;padding:11px;margin-top:8px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#1d4ed8,#2563eb);border:none;border-radius:10px;color:#fff;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;cursor:pointer;font-family:inherit;transition:.18s;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;gap:7px;box-shadow:0 3px 12px rgba(37,99,235,0.3);}
.btn-extract:hover{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#1e40af,#1d4ed8);transform:translateY(-1px);}
.btn-extract:disabled{opacity:.45;cursor:not-allowed;transform:none;}
.btn-reset{width:100%;padding:9px;background:#f1f5f9;border:1px solid var(--border-s);border-radius:10px;color:var(--muted);font-size:12px;cursor:pointer;margin-top:8px;font-family:inherit;transition:.15s;}
.btn-reset:hover{background:#e2e8f0;}
.output-panel{padding:20px 22px 40px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:14px;overflow-y:auto;background:var(--bg);}
.msg-placeholder{padding:52px 20px;text-align:center;color:var(--faint);}
.msg-placeholder-icon{font-size:2.4rem;margin-bottom:12px;}
.msg-placeholder-title{font-size:15px;font-weight:500;color:var(--muted);margin-bottom:8px;}
.msg-placeholder-sub{font-size:12px;line-height:1.7;}
/* ══ VALIDATION PANEL ══ */
.validation-panel{background:#fff;border:2px solid #f97316;border-radius:var(--radius);overflow:hidden;box-shadow:0 4px 20px rgba(249,115,22,0.15);animation:fadeUp .25s ease;}
.vp-header{padding:12px 16px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#fff7ed,#ffedd5);border-bottom:1px solid #fed7aa;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;}
.vp-icon{font-size:22px;}
.vp-title{font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:#9a3412;}
.vp-subtitle{font-size:11px;color:#c2410c;margin-top:2px;line-height:1.5;}
.vp-body{padding:14px 16px;}
.vp-missing-list{list-style:none;padding:0;margin:0 0 12px 0;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:8px;}
.vp-missing-item{display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:10px;padding:10px 12px;border-radius:8px;}
.vp-missing-item.critical{background:#fff1f2;border:1px solid #fecdd3;}
.vp-missing-item.warning{background:#fffbeb;border:1px solid #fde68a;}
.vp-field-icon{font-size:15px;flex-shrink:0;margin-top:2px;}
.vp-field-name{font-size:12px;font-weight:700;display:block;margin-bottom:2px;}
.vp-missing-item.critical .vp-field-name{color:#9f1239;}
.vp-missing-item.warning .vp-field-name{color:#92400e;}
.vp-field-hint{font-size:10px;color:#a16207;line-height:1.5;}
.vp-missing-item.critical .vp-field-hint{color:#be123c;}
.vp-inline-edit{margin-top:7px;}
.vp-inline-label{font-size:10px;font-weight:600;color:#64748b;display:block;margin-bottom:3px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.05em;}
.vp-inline-input{width:100%;padding:6px 10px;border:1px solid #e2e8f0;border-radius:6px;font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace;font-size:12px;background:#fff;color:#0f172a;outline:none;transition:.15s;}
.vp-inline-input:focus{border-color:var(--emerald);box-shadow:0 0 0 3px var(--emerald-x);}
.vp-inline-input.err{border-color:#f97316 !important;}
.vp-inline-input.ok{border-color:#22c55e !important;}
.vp-save-btn{width:100%;padding:11px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#f97316,#ea580c);border:none;border-radius:9px;color:#fff;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;cursor:pointer;font-family:inherit;transition:.18s;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;gap:8px;box-shadow:0 3px 12px rgba(249,115,22,0.3);}
.vp-save-btn:hover{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#ea580c,#c2410c);transform:translateY(-1px);}
.vp-preview-note{font-size:11px;color:var(--faint);text-align:center;padding:8px 0 0;font-style:italic;}
/* ══ FLIGHT CARD — NEW DESIGN ══ */
@keyframes fadeUp{from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(-6px)}to{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0)}}
.flight-card-wrap{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:14px;}

/* Outer card */
.flight-seg-card{background:var(--white);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:var(--radius);overflow:hidden;box-shadow:var(--shadow);animation:fadeUp .22s ease;}

/* Card header */
.fsc-header{padding:10px 16px;background:#f8fafc;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;}
.fsc-header-left{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;}
.fsc-trip-badge{font-size:10px;font-weight:700;padding:3px 10px;border-radius:20px;}
.fsc-trip-badge.oneway{background:#dbeafe;color:#1d4ed8;}
.fsc-trip-badge.roundtrip{background:#dcfce7;color:#166534;}
.fsc-trip-badge.multicity{background:#ede9fe;color:#6d28d9;}
.fsc-trip-badge.stopover{background:#fef3c7;color:#92400e;}
.fsc-seg-counter{font-size:10px;font-weight:600;color:var(--muted);background:#f1f5f9;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:20px;padding:2px 9px;font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace;}
.fsc-header-right{font-size:11px;color:var(--muted);}

/* Segment rows */
.fsc-segments{}
.fsc-seg-row{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 70px 1fr;align-items:center;padding:14px 16px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);}
.fsc-seg-row:last-child{border-bottom:none;}
.fsc-port{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:2px;}
.fsc-port.right{align-items:flex-end;text-align:right;}
.fsc-iata{font-size:22px;font-weight:700;color:var(--slate);font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace;line-height:1;}
.fsc-city{font-size:11px;color:var(--muted);margin-top:1px;}
.fsc-time{font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:var(--text);font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace;}
.fsc-date-small{font-size:10px;color:var(--faint);}

/* Middle arrow */
.fsc-mid{display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:3px;}
.fsc-mid-line{display:flex;align-items:center;width:100%;}
.fsc-mid-dot{width:5px;height:5px;border-radius:50%;border:1.5px solid var(--border-s);flex-shrink:0;}
.fsc-mid-dash{flex:1;height:0.5px;background:var(--border-s);}
.fsc-mid-plane{font-size:13px;color:var(--muted);}
.fsc-mid-dur{font-size:10px;color:var(--muted);}
.fsc-mid-fn{font-size:10px;color:var(--muted);font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace;font-weight:600;}

/* Layover strip */
.fsc-layover{padding:6px 16px;background:#fffbeb;border-bottom:1px solid #fde68a;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:7px;}
.fsc-layover-icon{font-size:12px;}
.fsc-layover-text{font-size:11px;color:#92400e;font-weight:600;}

/* Return divider */
.fsc-return-div{padding:6px 16px;background:#f0fdf4;border-top:1px solid #bbf7d0;border-bottom:1px solid #bbf7d0;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:7px;}
.fsc-return-div-text{font-size:11px;color:#166534;font-weight:600;}

/* Card footer */
.fsc-footer{padding:0;background:#f8fafc;border-top:1px solid var(--border);}
.fsc-footer-dur{padding:7px 16px 5px;font-size:11px;color:#0f766e;background:#f0fdfa;border-bottom:1px solid #99f6e4;font-weight:600;}
.fsc-footer-bottom{padding:7px 16px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;}
.fsc-footer-left{font-size:11px;color:var(--muted);display:flex;align-items:center;gap:5px;}
.fsc-footer-copy{padding:4px 12px;background:transparent;border:1px solid var(--border-s);border-radius:7px;font-size:11px;cursor:pointer;color:var(--muted);font-family:inherit;transition:.15s;}
.fsc-footer-copy:hover{background:#f1f5f9;}
.quote-card{background:#fff;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:var(--radius);overflow:hidden;box-shadow:var(--shadow);}
.quote-card-hdr{padding:10px 16px;background:#f8fafc;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;}
.quote-card-title{font-size:12px;font-weight:500;color:var(--muted);display:flex;align-items:center;gap:7px;}
.lang-dot{width:7px;height:7px;border-radius:50%;flex-shrink:0;}
.copy-btn{padding:5px 13px;background:transparent;border:1px solid var(--border-s);border-radius:7px;font-size:11px;cursor:pointer;color:var(--muted);font-family:inherit;transition:.15s;}
.copy-btn:hover{background:#f1f5f9;color:var(--text);}
.copy-btn.primary{background:var(--slate);color:#fff;border-color:var(--slate);}
.copy-btn.primary:hover{background:var(--slate-mid);}
.copy-btn.green{background:var(--emerald);color:#fff;border-color:var(--emerald-d);}
.copy-btn.green:hover{background:var(--emerald-d);}
.msg-box{padding:14px 16px;font-size:13px;line-height:2;white-space:pre-wrap;color:var(--text);}
.copy-row{display:flex;gap:8px;}
.btn-copy-both{flex:1;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;gap:6px;padding:9px 12px;background:#f1f5f9;border:1px solid var(--border-s);border-radius:9px;font-family:inherit;font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:var(--slate);cursor:pointer;transition:.18s;}
.btn-copy-both:hover{background:#e2e8f0;}
.internal-fft-card{background:#0a0f1e;border-radius:var(--radius);overflow:hidden;box-shadow:var(--shadow);}
.internal-fft-hdr{padding:10px 16px;background:#0f172a;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(74,222,128,.15);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;}
.internal-fft-title{font-size:11px;font-weight:600;color:#4ade80;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.08em;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:7px;}
.internal-fft-body{padding:14px 16px;font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace;font-size:12px;line-height:1.85;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#4ade80;}
html[lang=en] [data-ar]{display:none!important;}
html[lang=ar] [data-en]{display:none!important;}
::-webkit-scrollbar{width:5px;height:5px;}
::-webkit-scrollbar-track{background:transparent;}
::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb{background:#cbd5e1;border-radius:3px;}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="app-shell">
  <aside class="icon-sidebar">
    <div class="sb-logo">✈</div>
    <div class="sb-icon active" data-tip="ترجمة الرحلات">🗺️</div>
    <div class="sb-spacer"></div>
    <div class="sb-icon" data-tip="إعادة ضبط" onclick="resetAll()" style="color:#ef4444;">↺</div>
    <div class="sb-version">v2.6</div>
  </aside>
  <div class="main-panel">
    <header class="topbar">
      <div class="topbar-title">
        <span class="topbar-badge">✈ FT</span>
        <h1 class="topbar-h"><span data-ar>محوّل <span>الرحلات</span></span><span data-en>Flight <span>Translator</span></span></h1>
      </div>
      <div class="pb-right">
        <div class="lang-toggle">
          <button class="lang-btn active" id="btnAr" onclick="setLang('ar')">عربي</button>
          <button class="lang-btn" id="btnEn" onclick="setLang('en')">English</button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </header>
    <div class="body-layout">
      <div class="input-panel">
        <div class="ip-section">
          <div class="ip-title">
            <div class="ip-title-dot" style="background:var(--emerald)"></div>
            <span data-ar>نص الرحلة</span><span data-en>Flight Text</span>
          </div>
          <details class="fmt-helper" id="fmtHelper">
            <summary><span data-ar>▸ أمثلة الصيغ المدعومة</span><span data-en>▸ Supported format examples</span></summary>
            <div class="fmt-tabs" id="fmtTabs"></div>
            <div id="fmtExamples"></div>
          </details>
          <div id="parseStatus"></div>
          <textarea id="rawSeg" class="ip-textarea"
            placeholder="SV373 V 15JUN 1 JEDCMN HK1 0825 1305&#10;&#10;أو:&#10;G9 598 | CAI/SHJ | 20 MAY 2026 | 22:25 → 02:50"
            oninput="_debouncedInput(this.value)"></textarea>
          <button id="extractBtn" class="btn-extract" onclick="doExtract()" disabled>
            <span>📤</span>
            <span data-ar>ترجمة الرحلة</span><span data-en>Translate Flight</span>
          </button>
          <button class="btn-reset" onclick="resetAll()">
            <span data-ar>↺ إعادة ضبط</span><span data-en>↺ Reset</span>
          </button>
        </div>
        <div class="ip-section">
          <div class="ip-title">
            <div class="ip-title-dot" style="background:var(--amber)"></div>
            <span data-ar>نصائح</span><span data-en>Tips</span>
          </div>
          <div style="font-size:11px;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.9;">
            <div data-ar>✅ يدعم Amadeus GDS الكامل<br>✅ فلاي ديل، طيران ناس، العربية<br>✅ الصيغة المختصرة G9 598 | CAI/SHJ<br>✅ نص عربي ونص حر<br>✅ رحلات متعددة وذهاب وعودة ومع توقف<br>✅ يدعم جداول GDS وكتل DEP/ARR والنص العربي المنظم<br>✅ يدعم أوقات مساءً/صباحاً<br>✅ في حال نقص بيانات، يُطلب التعديل قبل العرض</div>
            <div data-en>✅ Full Amadeus GDS format<br>✅ Flyadeal, flynas, Air Arabia<br>✅ Short format G9 598 | CAI/SHJ<br>✅ Arabic & free text<br>✅ Multi-segment & round-trip<br>✅ Missing data prompts inline correction before display</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="output-panel" id="outputPanel">
        <div id="placeholder">
          <div class="msg-placeholder">
            <div class="msg-placeholder-icon">🗺️</div>
            <div class="msg-placeholder-title"><span data-ar>الصق نص الرحلة للبدء</span><span data-en>Paste flight text to begin</span></div>
            <div class="msg-placeholder-sub"><span data-ar>يدعم جميع صيغ الطيران الشائعة</span><span data-en>Supports all common airline formats</span></div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div id="results" style="display:none;flex-direction:column;gap:14px;"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>




<script>
let _debounceTimer = null;

function _debouncedInput(value){
  clearTimeout(_debounceTimer);

  _debounceTimer = setTimeout(() => {
    if (typeof smartExtract === "function") {
      try {
        smartExtract(value);
      } catch (e) {
        console.error("smartExtract error:", e);
      }
    }
  }, 300);
}
</script>

</body>
</html>
